## Who We Are
We are the driving force behind Trengx, a revolutionary approach to implementing Adaptive Transformers in IoT applications. Originating in 2023 as a visionary concept to address the dynamic nature of IoT environments using FaaS (FPGA-as-a-Service), Trengx now stands as a disruptive technology with an aim of serving millions of IoT users, ensuring efficient and real-time data processing.

Since our inception, we have held firm to the principles of remote work, open source, and continuous iteration. Every day, we collaborate with the Trengx community, delivering state-of-the-art solutions every month to assist our users to focus on their core applications and not on the complexities of underlying technology.

***

## What We Value

### People First
At Trengx, we place human beings at the heart of all our endeavors, prioritizing their well-being and prosperity above mere profit or technological advancement. Our ultimate purpose is to enrich the lives of all individuals, without discrimination, by delivering exceptional value that transcends barriers and uplifts humanity as a whole.

### Results with Purpose
Driven by a sense of purpose, we operate with urgency and a relentless bias for action, ensuring our promises are not just fulfilled, but exceed expectations for our team, customers, users, and valued investors.

### Customer Centric 
Our heartbeat resonates with the pulse of our customers. We start with them, immerse ourselves in their world, earning their trust, and obsessing over their delight, going above and beyond to exceed their dreams.

### Ownership Amplified
We hold the mantle of ownership, thinking beyond the horizon, acting with the holistic view of the entire company, going the extra mile, for no task is too small or beyond our scope.

### Synergistic Collaboration
We harness the power of synergy, promoting positive intent, expressing gratitude, and providing timely feedback to amplify the collective intelligence of our team.

### Iterative Innovators
Embracing the art of iteration, we focus on delivering the smallest viable and valuable components, constantly evolving based on insightful feedback, ensuring we stay ahead of the curve.

### Embrace Diversity, Empower Belonging
We create a tapestry of diversity, inclusion, and belonging, fostering an environment where individuals from all walks of life can thrive, share their unique perspectives, and feel genuinely valued.

### Transparency Unleashed
Our foundation rests on the bedrock of transparency, where openness flows like a river, from our public company handbook to sharing our technological prowess with the world, empowering collaboration and progress.

### Standards of Excellence
The pursuit of greatness is etched into our DNA. Relentlessly raising the bar, we cultivate a culture of perfection, where quality is the ultimate virtue, defects are eradicated, and problems are vanquished, never to resurface.
